     <td style="width:467.5pt; padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt" valign="top" width="472"><img alt="email pic" src="{[devName:email_pic]}" style="max-width: 1177.8240783691406px" title="email pic" /><br /> <span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:Barlow">16<sup>th</sup> September 2020</span></span></span></span><br /> <br /> <b><span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Barlow Medium&quot;"><span style="color:#37b359">UK Retail – How to help</span></span></span></b><br /> <br /> <span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:Barlow">Dear Retailer/Partner,</span></span><br /> <br /> <span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:Barlow">Like you, we were shocked at the UK government’s decision to withdraw the </span></span><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><a href="http://mx2.planetpayment.com:32224/?dmVyPTEuMDAxJiY3MmY4ZTcwYTY1YTc4MDExMj01RjYyMDc1Ml83MDM3OF8xNzA1OV8xJiY0M2NlYWZiOWFlMDdlZjA9MTIzMyYmdXJsPWh0dHBzJTNBJTJGJTJGcXVlc3Rpb25zLXN0YXRlbWVudHMlMkVwYXJsaWFtZW50JTJFdWslMkZ3cml0dGVuLXN0YXRlbWVudHMlMkZkZXRhaWwlMkYyMDIwLTA5LTExJTJGaGN3czQ0OCUyRQ==" style="color:blue; text-decoration:underline"><span style="font-family:Barlow"><span style="color:#0563c1">VAT Retail Export Scheme</span></span></a></span></span><br /> &nbsp;</span></span></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td style="width:467.5pt; padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt" valign="top" width="472"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><b><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:Barlow">We fail to understand the decision that has been made.&nbsp; </span></span></b><br /> <br /> <span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:Barlow">It comes at a time when UK Retail must be helped more than ever before.&nbsp; Instead, this action will be the opposite.&nbsp; It will take away your Tax Free revenues, and it will further hurt Travel &amp; Tourism.</span></span><br /> <br /> <span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:Barlow">Please rest assured that we are working with industry leaders to build a response and a far-reaching campaign.&nbsp; The first initial actions of this have already been put into action.</span></span><br /> <span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:Barlow">Alongside our partners such as AIR and NWEC, we are part of a powerful consortium aiming to reach and influence policy decision makers, politicians, and national, broadcast and trade media. </span></span><br /> <br /> <span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:Barlow">We are working together to protect jobs across Retail and beyond, to increase the UK’s competitive advantage, and to improve our nation’s economic health, both now and in the long term.</span></span><br /> &nbsp;</span></span></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td style="width:467.5pt; padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt" valign="top" width="472"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><b><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:Barlow">Our collective aim is to reverse the government’s decision to abolish Tax Free shopping in the UK for all countries.</span></span></b><br /> <br /> <span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:Barlow">Attached is the consortium’s briefing document, which outlines the key proof points that support our aim.&nbsp; In summary:</span></span></span></span> 
      <ul> 
       <li><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="tab-stops:list 36.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:Barlow">The government’s decision leaves a gaping hole in the UK economy, and encourage international tourists to spend their money anywhere but in the UK</span></span></span></span></span></li> 
       <li><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="tab-stops:list 36.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:Barlow">On top of COVID-19 ravaging our economy and the lives and families across the UK retail sector, this is a £5.6 billion hit being forced onto the UK economy</span></span></span></span></span></li> 
       <li><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="tab-stops:list 36.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:Barlow">It is at odds with the government’s stated ambitions for a “Global Britain”, with wider ramifications for Travel &amp; Tourism, and Hospitality</span></span></span></span></span></li> 
       <li><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="tab-stops:list 36.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:Barlow">From 1<sup>st</sup> January, UK citizens will be encouraged to shop Tax Free across the EU rather than spend in the UK</span></span></span></span></span></li> 
       <li><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="tab-stops:list 36.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:Barlow">Total annual spending by international visitors in the UK is over £22 billion, so we fail to understand why a decision would be made to reduce tourism in any way</span></span></span></span></span></li> 
       <li style="margin-bottom:11px"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="tab-stops:list 36.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:Barlow">We are taking legal advice on how best to examine the process that led to this decision</span></span></span></span></span></li> 
      </ul> <br /> <span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><b><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:Barlow">What you can do to help</span></span></b></span></span> 
